Come on boy, hello boy.

366
00:21:22,905 --> 00:21:24,230
你怎么样啊
How are you aye, hello.

367
00:21:24,456 --> 00:21:26,576
Jasper 这儿
Jasper. Here.

368
00:21:33,295 --> 00:21:34,271
我认识你们吗?
Do I know you?

369
00:21:34,308 --> 00:21:38,310
不 但显然Jasper认识你
No, but evidently, Jasper knows you.

370
00:21:38,347 --> 00:21:40,271
你一定是Sandy Bain
You must be Sandy Bain.

371
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:41,768
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

372
00:21:41,805 --> 00:21:44,337
是你上周把Jasper送到旅店的
It was you that brought Jasper to the tavern last week.

373
00:21:44,375 --> 00:21:46,105
是的
That's right.

374
00:21:46,410 --> 00:21:47,741
你喜欢动物吗?
You're fond of animals?

375
00:21:47,777 --> 00:21:49,520
它们都由上帝所造 先生
They're all God's creatures, sir.

376
00:21:49,558 --> 00:21:51,626
我不愿看到它们受伤害
I won't see no harm come to them.

377
00:21:51,663 --> 00:21:52,810
Mason先生似乎认为
Mr. Mason seemed to think

378
00:21:52,848 --> 00:21:55,349
Jasper幸运的逃脱了
that Jasper had a lucky escape.

379
00:21:55,386 --> 00:21:56,465
他那么做
He must have had a reason

380
00:21:56,503 --> 00:21:57,617
一定是有原因的
for behaving like he did.

381
00:21:57,653 --> 00:21:59,960
我相信Robert爵士的确有他的动机
I'm sure Sir Robert had the best of motives.

382
00:21:59,998 --> 00:22:02,366
不 我是说Jasper
No, I'm talking about Jasper.

383
00:22:02,404 --> 00:22:04,886
他一直很安静
He's always such a quiet dog.

384
00:22:04,924 --> 00:22:07,038
一定是发生了什么
Well, something must have happened to him.

385
00:22:07,076 --> 00:22:08,449
在那磨坊里?
At the millhouse?

386
00:22:08,486 --> 00:22:09,393
不 先生
No, sir.

387
00:22:09,430 --> 00:22:10,376
地下室?
The cellar?

388
00:22:10,413 --> 00:22:13,497
不 先生 是在老教堂里
No, sir, at the old church.

389
00:22:13,535 --> 00:22:15,027
事情就发生在我把它送去
It was the same morning

390
00:22:15,065 --> 00:22:17,291
Green Dragon旅店的那天早上
I brought him to the Green Dragon.

391
00:22:18,463 --> 00:22:20,732
那是个破旧损毁的小礼拜堂
It's an old ruin chapel,

392
00:22:20,770 --> 00:22:21,867
下面有个地下室
and under it there's a crypt

393
00:22:21,904 --> 00:22:24,262
在本地声名并不好
which has a bad name among us.

394
00:22:28,353 --> 00:22:30,092
Jasper
Jasper.

395
00:22:31,749 --> 00:22:32,731
别过去
Not that way.

396
